list.name: Default
list.comment:
Beam Calc V1.2B
New feature: - A mathematical term showing the process of the calculation can be displayed with the solution.
- Support names are displayed now.
- Improved resolution and size of the drawing showing the beam and the solution.
Polished: - Load list, index of loads is set according to line or single load (q1,F1,q2,F2....).
- Load list: Changed layout to work better on smaller screens. Loads are displayed in a horizontal scroll view now.
- Replaced checkboxes by icons. That way more options do fit into the upper half of the screen.
- Back button check. When pressed once and then switched to another activity, after returning the number of times the button was pressed was forgotten. Changed that.
Reorganized source code.
- Moved beamCalc class library into the lib's folder. Added latest version of the beamCalc class library.
- Moved classes associated with the fileDialog- tool to an external repositorylocated on gitHub.
Library's
- Added locale en to FileDialog tool
